Hand lettered in casual script and festive typography with plenty of space for you to introduce your new baby, include birth stats and your christmas wishes. The photo template is set up for you to add 4 photos, one on the front and three on the back. Your photos are displayed in vertical portrait and horizontal landscape format so, if you have any problems with placement, try cropping your picture to the relevant shape and re-uploading or click "edit using design tool" to reposition anything.
